Hibernate Validator 4.0.2 is now available for <a href="https://www.hibernate.org/6.html" target="" class="regularLink">download</a>. This release was necessary for the JCP integration efforts for <a href="http://jcp.org/en/jsr/detail?id=303" target="" class="regularLink">JSR-303</a> and addresses a potential NullPointerException (<a href="http://opensource.atlassian.com/projects/hibernate/browse/HV-263" target="" class="regularLink">HV-263</a>).
Refer to the 4.0.2 <a href="http://opensource.atlassian.com/projects/hibernate/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10060&amp;version=10982" target="" class="regularLink">release notes</a> for a full list of changes. 
</p>

